Outcome: GREEN. 41/41 tests across the codegen family (bucket 7 +
         projection 19 + pipeline 15; was 35, +6 new).

What landed (additive within our own codegen family):
  crates/op-codegen-projection/src/lib.rs
    - New pub enum ColumnKind { Any, Int }
    - New impls: ColumnKind::infer(field_name) -> Self
                 ColumnKind::surreal_token(self) -> &'static str
    - DefineField gains pub kind: ColumnKind
    - project() fills kind via ColumnKind::infer at DefineField construction
    - surreal_text(): emits TYPE <kind> for required, TYPE option<<kind>>
